==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[#Latin|creator]]'', agent noun from perfect passive participle ''[[creatus]]'' (created), from verb ''[[creare]]'' (create) + agent suffix ''[[or]]''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# one who [[create]]s or makes something
#: ''Kenneth E. Iverson was the '''creator''' of APL.''

